<item>
            <title>[LU-11843] customise sanity-quota to work with project quotas set before the suite</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11843</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-quota enables project quotas by the following way :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;stopall()-&amp;gt;tune2fs &amp;lt;dev&amp;gt; -&amp;gt; setupall&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need the possibility to run sanity-quota on the system with project quotas enabled before the tests (the case for real clusters) and not disable it after tests completed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
